{{Top|leg}}
"'''Catching the wind'''" was a phrase referring to the effect the [[Spice/Legends|spice]] particles in the [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] of [[Sevarcos II]] had on newcomers to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] who did not wear protective masks.

